 Array: It is a collection of elements of same data type.
 Syntax to create array:
        data-type arran_name[] = new data_type[array_size];
 Example: int number = new int[5];
 Note: In array, the total index value is calculated by
           total index value = arrray.length - 1;
 
 Advantages of an array:
  i. Code optimization: sort the data efficiently.
 ii. Random access: can get any data located at any index position.
 
 Disadvantage of an array:
